<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/head')%>
<body>

  <!-- Lets put some stuff on the page -->

  <!-- Here shall be the navigation bar! -->
  <%- include('../partials/header')%>

  <!-- Section to display past works -->
  <main id="main-content">
    <h1>Commissions</h1>
    <section id="info-section">
      <h3>Please read this important information!</h3>
      <p>Before selecting your products, please take some time to read through my <a href="./policy">Policy</a> to answer some basic questions and familiarize yourself with the process!</p>
      <p>*All prices are in USD. Payments are made via PayPal.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="commission-section">
      <article class="showcase-item">
        <h2>Twitch Stream Package</h2>
        <h3>$120</h3>
        <hr>
        <h3>A set of essential elements for your stream</h3>
        <figure>  
          <ul>
            <li>1 Simple Overlay, 3 Scenes and 6 Panels.</li>
            <li>Includes PNG files: (1920x1080)(320x100) etc.</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/MrzMami-Basic-Scenes-Package-with-Banners.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Twitch Stream Package please!')">Stream Package</a>
        <hr>
      </article>

      <article class="showcase-item">
        <h2>Emotes</h2>
        <h3>1x $30 || 3x $90 || 6x $180</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <li>Includes PNG Files: (500x500px) image for upload.</li>
            <li>$15 for seasonal/holiday modifications.</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/Emote-Spread.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Single Emote please!')">Single Emote</a>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Pack of 3 Emotes please!')">3 Emotes</a>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Pack of 6 Emotes please!')">6 Emotes</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

      <article class="showcase-item">
        <h2>Subscriber & Bit Badges</h2>
        <h3>1x $20-30 || 3x $75 || 6x $150</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <h4>Unique Styles $30/ea</h4>
            <li>Each badge is different from the last with changes in line art or completely new images.</li>
            <h4>Recolor Style $20/ea</h4>
            <li>Badges vary in appearance with color changes, but the line art remains the same.</li>
            <li>Includes 3 sizes for Twitch (72px, 36px, 18px)</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/NoaimDontFlame-Sub-Badges.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Single Sub Badge please!')">Single Badge</a>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Pack of 3 Sub Badges please!')">3 Badges</a>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Pack of 6 Sub Badges please!')">6 Badges</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

      <article class="showcase-item">
        <h2>Basic Scenes, Overlays or Banners</h2>
        <h3>1x $20 || 6x $110</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <li>*Starting Soon, Be Right Back/Intermission, Just Chatting, Stream Ending, Offline, etc</li>
            <li>Includes PNG Files: (1920x1080 Other resolutions must be discussed prior to ordering.</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/ThePluckyAvatar-Scene-Set.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Single Scene, Overlay or Banner please!')">Single Item</a>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Pack of 6 Scenes, Overlays or Banners please!')">6 Items</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

      <article class="showcase-item">
        <h2>Illustrated Scene</h2>
        <h3>$80 - $150 / Scene</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <li>*Scenes are hand-drawn and can include characters, background, and other misc. objects.</li>
            <li>Prices will vary based on complexity and level of detail.</li>
            <li>Includes PNG Files(1920x1080) Other resolutions must be discussed prior to ordering.</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/CadesArcade-Illustrated-Scene.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Illustrated Scene please!')">Illustrated Scene</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

      

      <article class="showcase-item">
        <h2>Basic Panels</h2>
        <h3>1x $10 || 6x $60</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <li>*Panels only change text +/or color. Your mascots or logos can be added as a feature.</li>
            <li>An  "Artist" or "Credit" panel can be made free of charge.</li>
            <li>IncludesPNG Files: (320x100)</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/Sample-Set-Twitch-Panels.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Single Basic Panel please!')">Single Panel</a>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Pack of 6 Basic Panels please!')">6 Panels</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

      <article class="showcase-item">
        <h2>Illustrated Panels</h2>
        <h3>$30/ea</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <li>*Panels are hand drawn and can include any subject you like/Mascots and logos can be included as a feature.</li>
            <li>Prices will vary based on complexity and level of detail.</li>
            <li>Includes PNG Files(1920x1080) Other resolutions must be discussed prior to ordering.</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/Notorious_BLT-Illustrated-Panels.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Illustrated Panels please!')">Illustrated Panels</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

      <article class="showcase-item">
        <h2>Decorative Stream Schedule</h2>
        <h3>$40</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <li>*Can be designed for other purposes as well.</li>
            <li>Dimensions: (2050x780)</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/DesertWhale-Schedule.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Decorative Stream Schedule!')">Stream Schedule</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

      <article class="showcase-item smaller">
        <h2>Poster or Graphic</h2>
        <h3>$30</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <li>Includes: 2 Revisions.</li>
            <li>PNG Files: (1920x1080) or requested size.</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/Raft-with-Friends-advert.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Poster or Graphic please!')">Poster/Graphic</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

      <article class="showcase-item smaller">
        <h2>Profile Picture / Avatar / Icon</h2>
        <h3>$35</h3>
        <hr>
        <figure>
          <ul>
            <li>*Visual references are required for portraits.</li>
            <li>Includes 1 custom Profile Picture. 2 Revisions. PNG Files: (800x800)</li>
          </ul>
          <img src="images/Jeremy-Hay-Character-Art.jpg" alt="Image" onContextMenu="return false;" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
        <div>
          <a href="#hire-section" onclick="addValue('Profile Picture, Avatar or Icon please!')">Prof. Pic., Avatar, Icon</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      </article>

        <!-- Contact/Hire form -->
        <section id="hire-section">
          <h2>Do you need some art done?</h2>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/TheDesertWhale" class="twit-link" target="_blank">Message me on Twitter!</a>
          <p>Or fill out the form below!</p>
    
          <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mqkwqgrg" method="post">
    
            <label for="fname">Name:</label><br>
            <input type="text" name="fname" placeholder="John Doe"><br>
    
            <label for="_replyto">Email:</label><br>
            <input type="email" name="_replyto" placeholder="johndoe@email.com" required><br>
    
            <label for="message">Your Order/Comments:</label><br>
            <textarea type="text" maxlength="150" cols="38" rows="4" name="message" id="comments" placeholder="Do you have a package(s) in mind?" required></textarea><br>
    
            <div>
              <input type="submit" value="Send">
              <input type="reset" value="Clear">
            </div>
            
    
            <p>*We will discuss terms and payment conditions after establishing the work to be done.</p>
          </form>
        </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Nothin to see here, just a footer. -->
  <%- include('../partials/footer')%>
</body>
</html>